Filtering Cells and Genes

In [134]:
# Filter cells
adata = adata[adata.obs['n_genes_by_counts'] < 6000, :]
adata = adata[adata.obs['pct_counts_mt'] < 5, :]

# Filter genes
sc.pp.filter_genes(adata, min_cells=3)

Normalization and Scaling

In [135]:
# Check if data is already normalized
if 'norm10k' in adata.layers:
    adata.X = adata.layers['norm10k']
else:
    # Normalize and log-transform the data
    sc.pp.normalize_total(adata, target_sum=1e4)
    sc.pp.log1p(adata)

Cell Type Annotation

Define Marker Genes

In [144]:
marker_genes_dict = {
    'Cycling Cells': ['NME2_hg38', 'TFDP1_hg38', 'CCNA2_hg38'],
    'Differentiating Progenitors': ['NDRG1_hg38', 'KDM4B_hg38'],
    'S-phase Cells': ['HJURP_hg38', 'SHCBP1_hg38', 'ESCO2_hg38'],
    'Stressed Cells': ['MT-RNR1_hg38', 'MT-RNR2_hg38', 'MT-ND5_hg38'],
    'Immune Cells': ['LRBA_hg38', 'PTK2_hg38', 'TRIO_hg38'],
    'Endothelial Cells': ['ADGRG6_hg38', 'CRIM1_hg38'],
    'Monocytes/Macrophages': ['CBR4_hg38', 'LRBA_hg38'],
    'Lymphocytes': ['CBL_hg38', 'APLP2_hg38'],
}

cell_type_map = {
    '0': 'Cycling Cells',
    '1': 'Differentiating Progenitors',
    '2': 'S-phase Cells',
    '3': 'Stressed Cells',
    '4': 'Cycling Cells',
    '5': 'Immune Cells',
    '6': 'Endothelial Cells',
    '7': 'Monocytes/Macrophages',
    '8': 'Lymphocytes',
}

adata.obs['cell_type'] = adata.obs['leiden'].map(cell_type_map)

Verify names

In [145]:
for gene_list in marker_genes_dict.values():
    for gene in gene_list:
        if gene not in adata.var_names:
            print(f"{gene} not found in adata.var_names")
